      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 335,
      "message": "The appc-client is used by SO, and it supports LCM APIs of both APPC and SDNC. The LCM APIs of SDNC support PNF, such as PNF software upgrade.\nTherefore, in order to call the new added DownloadNeSw and ActivateNeSw actions by SO for PNF software upgrade use case, I need to add supports for PNF to APPC (especially for appc-client).",
